The paper proposes a novel deep learning network for tabular data learning, which falls under the category of machine learning. Specifically, the network utilizes attention mechanisms and decision trees, which are commonly used in the sub-fields of deep learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and data structures (cs.DS). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
